input: I am hungry.
output: Men ochqaman.
expected: Men och qoldim.

input: She is my sister.
output: U mening singlim.
expected: U mening singlim.

input: The weather is cold today.
output: Bugun ob-havo sovuq.
expected: Bugun havo sovuq.

input: This is my house.
output: Bu mening uyim.
expected: Bu mening uyim.

input: We are friends.
output: Biz do‘stlarimiz.
expected: Biz do‘stmiz.

input: I want some water.
output: Menga bir oz suv kerak.
expected: Menga biroz suv kerak.

input: He is very tall.
output: U juda baland.
expected: U juda baland bo‘yli.

input: Where is the bus stop?
output: Avtobus bekatlari qayerda?
expected: Avtobus bekati qayerda?

input: I like your car.
output: Menga sizning mashinangiz yoqadi.
expected: Menga mashinangiz yoqdi.

input: My name is Ali.
output: Mening ismim Ali.
expected: Mening ismim Ali.

input: I go to the gym three times a week.
output: Men haftada uch marta sport zaliga boraman.
expected: Men haftasiga uch marta sport zaliga boraman.

input: Yesterday we went shopping at the mall.
output: Kecha biz savdo markaziga xarid qilishga bordik.
expected: Kecha biz savdo markaziga borib xarid qildik.

input: He speaks Uzbek, Russian, and English fluently.
output: U o‘zbek, rus va ingliz tillarini erkin gapiradi.
expected: U o‘zbek, rus va ingliz tillarida ravon gapiradi.

input: I forgot my wallet at home this morning.
output: Men ertalab hamyonimni uyda unutib ketdim.
expected: Ertalab hamyonimni uyda unutib qoldim.

input: My father works in a bank as a manager.
output: Mening otam bankda boshqaruvchi sifatida ishlaydi.
expected: Otam bankda menejer bo‘lib ishlaydi.

input: We are planning to visit Samarkand next month.
output: Biz kelasi oy Samarqandga sayohat qilishni rejalashtirmoqdamiz.
expected: Keyingi oy Samarqandga borishni rejalashtiryapmiz.

input: The train leaves at 8:30 in the morning.
output: Poyezl ertalab soat 8:30 da jo‘naydi.
expected: Poyezd ertalab soat 8:30 da jo‘naydi.

input: Please call me when you arrive.
output: Iltimos, yetib borganingizda menga qo‘ng‘iroq qiling.
expected: Yetib borganingizda iltimos, menga qo‘ng‘iroq qiling.

input: I don’t eat meat, but I like fish.
output: Men go‘sht yemayman, lekin baliqni yaxshi ko‘raman.
expected: Men go‘sht yemayman, lekin baliqni yaxshi ko‘raman.

input: There is a big park near my house.
output: Uyim yaqinida katta bog‘ bor.
expected: Uyim yonida katta bog‘ bor.

input: Education is the most powerful tool to change the world.
output: Ta’lim dunyoni o‘zgartirish uchun eng kuchli vosita.
expected: Ta’lim — dunyoni o‘zgartirishning eng kuchli vositasidir.

input: No matter how difficult the road is, we must keep moving forward.
output: Yo‘l qanchalik qiyin bo‘lmasin, biz oldinga harakatlanishda davom etishimiz kerak.
expected: Yo‘l qanchalik qiyin bo‘lmasin, biz oldinga yurishda davom etishimiz kerak.

input: He achieved success thanks to his patience and hard work.
output: U sabr va mehnat tufayli muvaffaqiyatga erishdi.
expected: U sabr-toqat va mehnati tufayli muvaffaqiyatga erishdi.

input: Freedom of speech is an important right in every society.
output: So‘z erkinligi har bir jamiyatda muhim huquqdir.
expected: So‘z erkinligi har bir jamiyatda muhim huquqdir.

input: The book discusses the impact of technology on human relationships.
output: Kitob texnologiyaning inson munosabatlariga taʼsirini muhokama qiladi.
expected: Kitob texnologiyaning inson munosabatlariga ta’sirini muhokama qiladi.

input: People should take responsibility for protecting the environment.
output: Odamlar atrof-muhitni himoya qilish mas’uliyatini o‘z zimmasiga olishi kerak.
expected: Odamlar atrof-muhitni asrash uchun mas’uliyatni o‘z zimmasiga olishi kerak.

input: True friendship is based on trust and honesty.
output: Haqiqiy do‘stlik ishonch va samimiyatga asoslanadi.
expected: Haqiqiy do‘stlik ishonch va halollikka asoslanadi.

input: Our history is full of lessons for future generations.
output: Bizning tariximiz kelajak avlodlar uchun saboqdur.
expected: Tariximiz kelajak avlodlar uchun saboqlarga boy.

input: In difficult times, unity is the key to overcoming challenges.
output: Qiyin paytlarda birlik qiyinchiliklarni yengish kaliti hisoblanadi.
expected: Qiyin paytlarda birlik sinovlarni yengishning kalitidir.

input: Success without ethics is an empty achievement.
output: Ahlokdan holi muvaffaqiyat bo‘sh yutuqdir.
expected: Axloqsiz muvaffaqiyat — bo‘sh yutuqdir.

input: The new processor architecture increases performance by reducing power consumption.
output: Yangi protsessor arxitekturasi elektr energiyasini kamaytirish orqali ishlash tezligini oshiradi.
expected: Yangi protsessor arxitekturasi quvvat sarfini kamaytirib, unumdorlikni oshiradi.

input: The laboratory uses high-precision instruments to conduct experiments.
output: Laboratoriya tajribalarni o‘tkazish uchun yuqqi aniqlikdagi asboblardan foydalanadi.
expected: Laboratoriya tajribalarni o‘tkazish uchun yuqori aniqlikdagi asboblardan foydalanadi.

input: Renewable energy sources can significantly reduce greenhouse gas emissions.
output: Yangilanuvchi energiya manbalari issiqxona gazlarining chiqishini sezilarli darajada kamaytirishi mumkin.
expected: Qayta tiklanuvchi energiya manbalari issiqxona gazlari chiqindilarini sezilarli kamaytirishi mumkin.

input: The robot is programmed to perform repetitive tasks without human intervention.
output: Robot odamning ishtirokisiz takrorlanuvchi vazifalarni bajarishga dasturlangan.
expected: Robot inson aralashuvisiz takrorlanuvchi vazifalarni bajarishga dasturlangan.

input: The software automatically backs up data to prevent loss.
output: Dasturiy ta’minot ma’lumotlarni yo‘qolishdan saqlash uchun avtomatik tarzda zaxira nusxa yaratadi.
expected: Dastur ma’lumotlarning yo‘qolishini oldini olish uchun avtomatik zaxiralashni amalga oshiradi.

input: The research team analyzed the impact of climate change on crop yields.
output: Tadqiqot guruhi iqlim o‘zgarishi dehqonchilik hosildorligiga taʼsirini tahlil qildi.
expected: Tadqiqot guruhi iqlim o‘zgarishining hosildorlikka ta’sirini tahlil qildi.

input: The device uses wireless communication to transmit sensor readings.
output: Qurilma sensor o‘qishlarini uzatish uchun simsiz aloqa tizimidan foydalanadi.
expected: Qurilma sensor o‘qishlarini uzatish uchun simsiz aloqa texnologiyasidan foydalanadi.

input: The experiment confirmed the accuracy of the theoretical model.
output: Tajriba nazariy modelning aniqligini tasdiqladi.
expected: Tajriba nazariy modelning aniqligini tasdiqladi.

input: The satellite continuously monitors weather patterns across the globe.
output: Sun’iy yo‘ldosh dunyo bo‘ylab ob-havo holatini doimiy monitoring qiladi.
expected: Sun’iy yo‘ldosh butun dunyo bo‘ylab ob-havo holatini uzluksiz kuzatib boradi.

input: The engineers developed a new algorithm to detect network intrusions.
output: Muhandislar tarmoq yonilg‘ilarini aniqlash uchun yangi algoritm ishlab chiqdilar.
expected: Muhandislar tarmoqdagi ruxsatsiz kirishlarni aniqlash uchun yangi algoritm ishlab chiqdi.

input: Bro, last nigh we partied hard till 4 a.m.
output: Do‘stim, kecha tunda soat 4 gacha qiziq o‘tdik.
expected: Jigar, kecha soat 4gacha dam oldik

input: My phone’s dead, can I borrow yours?
output: Mening telefonim o‘chib qoldi, senikini qarzga olsa bo‘ladimi?
expected: Meni telefonim o’chib qoldi, senikini olib tursam bo’ladimi?

input: Man, he talks big but never does anything.
output: Odam gap ko‘p, lekin hech narsa qilmaydi.
expected: U faqat gapirishi bilar ekan, qo’lidan hech narsa kelmas ekan.

input: Let’s grab some burgers after work.
output: Ishdan keyin bir oz burger yeylik.
expected: Ishdan kegin burger yemimizami.

input: Dude, your car is sick!
output: Do‘stim, mashinang zo‘r ekan!
expected: Jigar, moshinen zo’r ku!

input: I’m broke, can you cover me this time?
output: Mening hamyonim bo‘sh, bu safar sen toʻlab berolmaysanmi?
expected: Bir tingim yo’q, bus afar sen tolab yubora olasanmi?

input: She ghosted me after the second date.
output: U ikkinchi uchrashuvdan keyin meni bloklab qo‘ydi.
expected: Ikkinchi uchrashuvdan kegin, u meni bortimni berdi.

input: That deal is shady, I wouldn’t trust it.
output: Bu bitim shubhali, ishonmaslik yaxshi.
expected: Bu yerda bir gap bor, men ishonmas edim.

input: I’m starving, let’s hit the café.
output: Och qoldim, kafega kettik.
expected: Qornim rossa och, kafega kirsakchi.

input: The guy’s loaded, money isn’t an issue for him.
output: Odamda pul ko‘p, pul unga muammo emas.
expected: Bu bolani soqqasi ko’p, puldan muammo yo’q.
